            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>截至台北時間28日10:30，<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>上漲170.28點（或2.1%），暫報8287.46點。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li>近 1 週：+4.14%</li><li>近 1 月：+12.62%</li><li>近 3 月：+13.24%</li><li>近 6 月：+43.77%</li><li>今年以來：+14.6%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>焦點個股</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>成分股以英特爾(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:INTC:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/INTC\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">INTC-US</a>)領漲。英特爾(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:INTC:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/INTC\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">INTC-US</a>)上漲6.33%；超捷國際(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:MCHP:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/MCHP\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">MCHP-US</a>)上漲6.09%；Onto Innovation Inc.(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:ONTO:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/ONTO\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">ONTO-US</a>)上漲4.22%；德州儀器(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:TXN:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/TXN\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">TXN-US</a>)上漲3.64%；泰瑞達(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:TER:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/TER\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">TER-US</a>)上漲3.1%。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>部分成分股表現相對疲軟，思佳訊半導體(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:SWKS:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/SWKS\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">SWKS-US</a>)下跌8.87%；科沃(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:QRVO:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/QRVO\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">QRVO-US</a>)下跌7.62%；凌雲邏輯(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:CRUS:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/CRUS\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">CRUS-US</a>)下跌1.06%；高通(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:QCOM:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/QCOM\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">QCOM-US</a>)下跌0.92%。</p></section></main>",
